# API Response Envelope

> Source of truth: `00_API_CONVENTIONS.md`. Do NOT deviate from the envelope.

## Envelope (every response, success AND error)

```json
{
  "code": "SUCCESS",
  "message": "Operation completed",
  "status": 200,
  "data": { ... }
}
```

- `code` — UPPER_SNAKE_CASE business code (`SUCCESS`, `INVALID_GPS`, `RATE_LIMIT_EXCEEDED`).
- `message` — i18n via `Accept-Language` (`vi-VN` default, `en-US` supported).
- `status` — HTTP status (200/201/204/400/401/403/404/409/422/429/500/503).
- `data` — payload, `null` on errors without field info.

## Controller pattern

```csharp
[ApiController]
[Route("v1/[controller]")]
public sealed class ReportsController(ISender sender) : ControllerBase
{
    /// <summary>Submit a new pollution report.</summary>
    [HttpPost]
    [Authorize(Policy = Policies.CanSubmitReport)]
    [ProducesResponseType(typeof(ApiResponse<Guid>), StatusCodes.Status201Created)]
    [ProducesResponseType(typeof(ApiResponse<object>), StatusCodes.Status422UnprocessableEntity)]
    public async Task<IActionResult> SubmitAsync(
        [FromBody] SubmitReportCommand cmd,
        CancellationToken ct)
        => (await sender.Send(cmd, ct)).ToHttp();
}
```

## URL naming

- URL paths → `kebab-case` (`/pollution-reports`, `/cleanup-tasks`).
- Query params → `camelCase` (`?pageSize=20&sortBy=createdAt&sortOrder=desc`).
- JSON keys → `camelCase`. Enum JSON values → `UPPER_SNAKE_CASE`.

## Pagination — mandatory on all list endpoints

```
GET /v1/reports?page=1&pageSize=20&sortBy=createdAt&sortOrder=desc
```

- `page` 1-indexed, `pageSize` default 20, max 100.
- Response: `{ items, pagination: { page, pageSize, totalItems, totalPages, hasNext, hasPrev } }`.
- Cursor-based preferred for very large datasets.

## Auth headers

```
Authorization: Bearer {accessToken}
Accept-Language: vi-VN
X-Request-ID: {uuid}            # server generates if absent
```

## Rate limit headers (always present)

```
X-RateLimit-Limit: 60
X-RateLimit-Remaining: 45
X-RateLimit-Reset: 1715234600
Retry-After: 30                 # only on 429
```

## Common business codes

`SUCCESS`, `VALIDATION_ERROR`, `UNAUTHORIZED`, `FORBIDDEN`, `NOT_FOUND`, `CONFLICT`, `RATE_LIMIT_EXCEEDED`, `INTERNAL_ERROR`, `SERVICE_UNAVAILABLE`, `INVALID_GPS`, `OUT_OF_VIETNAM`, `IMAGE_TOO_LARGE`, `TOO_MANY_IMAGES`, `INVALID_STATE_TRANSITION`, `DUPLICATE_REPORT`, `INVALID_CREDENTIALS`, `ACCOUNT_LOCKED`, `OTP_EXPIRED`, `AI_UNAVAILABLE`, `AI_TIMEOUT`.
